## üö® Critical Warnings

### **TIER 3 ASSETS - USE WITH EXTREME CAUTION:**

#### **NGAS (Natural Gas):**
- ‚ö†Ô∏è 5-10% daily swings
- ‚ö†Ô∏è Weather-driven (unpredictable)
- ‚ö†Ô∏è Weekly storage reports cause chaos
- ‚ö†Ô∏è Only trade during consolidation periods
- **Recommendation:** Disable unless experienced

#### **TSLA (Tesla):**
- ‚ö†Ô∏è 3-8% daily volatility
- ‚ö†Ô∏è Elon Musk tweets = random gaps
- ‚ö†Ô∏è Earnings shocks every 90 days
- ‚ö†Ô∏è Exit before 3PM to avoid overnight gaps
- **Recommendation:** Small position (3% max)

#### **BTC/ETH (Crypto):**
- ‚ö†Ô∏è 2-8% daily volatility
- ‚ö†Ô∏è 24/7 markets = weekend gap risk
- ‚ö†Ô∏è Manipulation by whales
- ‚ö†Ô∏è Regulatory news = instant crashes
- **Recommendation:** Only when score ‚â•90

